# 🔐 Sign-in Risk Policy (P2)

---

### Policy Summary

#### **Purpose:**

Block or challenge risky login attempts.

---

#### **Activities Matching Criteria:**

* Sign-in risk = Medium/High

---

#### **Actions:**

* Require MFA or block

---

## 🎯 Use Cases

* Impossible travel
* Anonymous IP login

---

## 🛡️ How This Protects Identity

* Stops suspicious authentication in real-time

---

